headline: Thinkific Reimagines Learning Commerce With Agentic AI Features and Strategic Brand Refresh
summary: Thinkific Labs Inc. (TSX: THNC), a leading learning commerce platform, today announced a strategic rebrand and major product investments designed to fuel customer growth through courses, community, and commerce. This evolution, which includes new and upcoming AI powered features, is designed to meet the growing demand from businesses looking to monetize expertise through scalable, education-based revenue models.

headline: Calamos Phineus Long/Short Fund Q1 2025 Commentary
summary: Calamos Phineus Long/Short Fund rose 0.93% in Q1 (Class I shares at NAV), compared with a price decline of -4.27% for the S&P 500 Index and loss of -2.15% for the MSCI World Index.
